1
00:00:10,100 --> 00:00:11,600
There are no guards.

2
00:00:11,600 --> 00:00:13,467
I don't see any people.

3
00:00:13,467 --> 00:00:16,633
Samuel, the scam warehouse is
crawling with guards!

4
00:00:18,333 --> 00:00:19,500
Roldan's not here.

5
00:00:19,500 --> 00:00:20,700
What's going on?!

6
00:00:21,733 --> 00:00:23,467
Sir, they beat us to it.

7
00:00:23,467 --> 00:00:26,000
Agnes just sent
the distress code.

8
00:00:26,000 --> 00:00:27,100
Get out of there.

9
00:00:27,100 --> 00:00:28,633
It's a trap! Hurry!

10
00:00:29,333 --> 00:00:30,267
[GUNSHOT]

11
00:00:39,167 --> 00:00:40,500
Toss him in the trunk.

12
00:00:48,600 --> 00:00:50,767
This is just
the beginning, Samuel.

13
00:00:50,767 --> 00:00:52,333
Once I'm done with you,

14
00:00:52,333 --> 00:00:57,767
you will wish you never meddled
 in my business!

15
00:01:10,467 --> 00:01:13,133
All units. 10-12. Hold positio.

16
00:01:13,667 --> 00:01:15,667
The reconnaissance is
still underway.

17
00:01:15,667 --> 00:01:17,167
What exactly is going on?

18
00:01:22,033 --> 00:01:24,400
Miss! Miss, this is Agnes!

19
00:01:24,400 --> 00:01:25,500
Let's go!

20
00:01:25,500 --> 00:01:26,467
Hey!

21
00:01:30,833 --> 00:01:33,500
Agnes, let's go! Come on!

22
00:01:41,367 --> 00:01:42,500
Hello, Samuel?

23
00:01:42,500 --> 00:01:44,167
Are you going to pick up Chloe?

24
00:01:44,167 --> 00:01:45,500
Why, Samuel? What's happening?

25
00:01:46,200 --> 00:01:47,833
My cover has been blown.

26
00:01:47,833 --> 00:01:49,833
Look, I know you're not part
of the syndicate.

27
00:01:49,833 --> 00:01:51,533
So, if you're heading
to the school,

28
00:01:51,533 --> 00:01:53,433
you need to protect our son.

29
00:01:53,433 --> 00:01:55,200
Please take King.

30
00:01:55,200 --> 00:01:58,333
Who would want to kill my son?

31
00:01:59,833 --> 00:02:01,500
Is it Jacob?

32
00:02:01,500 --> 00:02:02,533
Not just him.

33
00:02:02,533 --> 00:02:04,500
Leah, we're talking
about your father too.

34
00:02:05,433 --> 00:02:06,733
They're in cahoots.

35
00:02:09,867 --> 00:02:16,800
[THEME MUSIC PLAYING]

36
00:02:34,800 --> 00:02:35,800
[TENSE MUSIC PLAYING]

37
00:02:35,800 --> 00:02:37,467
- Come here!
- Let me go!

38
00:02:37,467 --> 00:02:38,300
Please don't!

39
00:02:38,300 --> 00:02:40,100
[GOON 1]
You're being a pain, kid!

40
00:02:40,100 --> 00:02:41,700
- Let me go!
- Come here!

41
00:02:41,700 --> 00:02:45,133
- Get your hands off me!
- Just come with us!

42
00:02:45,133 --> 00:02:46,733
- [LEAH] King!
- Let me go!

43
00:02:46,733 --> 00:02:49,367
- [KICKS LANDING]
- [KING CRYING]

44
00:02:50,300 --> 00:02:51,767
[BREATHING HEAVILY]

45
00:02:51,767 --> 00:02:55,800
[TENSE MUSIC CONTINUES]

46
00:02:55,800 --> 00:02:57,700
- [GOON 2] Who are you?!
- Step back!

47
00:02:58,400 --> 00:02:59,600
Stay right here!

48
00:02:59,600 --> 00:03:05,400
- [LEAH GRUNTING]
- [BLOWS, KICKS LANDING]

49
00:03:05,400 --> 00:03:07,733
[KING] Please let me go!

50
00:03:07,733 --> 00:03:08,633
King!

51
00:03:08,633 --> 00:03:11,233
- [LEAH GRUNTING]
- [BLOW, KICK LAND]

52
00:03:11,233 --> 00:03:12,600
[TENSE MUSIC CONTINUES]

53
00:03:12,600 --> 00:03:13,800
King!

54
00:03:13,800 --> 00:03:15,300
Is that Leah?!

55
00:03:15,300 --> 00:03:16,467
[LEAH GRUNTING]

56
00:03:17,800 --> 00:03:19,133
[EXCLAIMS]

57
00:03:19,133 --> 00:03:20,233
- King!
- [KICK LANDS]

58
00:03:20,233 --> 00:03:21,233
[BODY THUDS]

59
00:03:24,167 --> 00:03:25,167
Agnes?!

60
00:03:25,800 --> 00:03:26,800
Leah?!

61
00:03:26,800 --> 00:03:28,433
You know how to fight?

62
00:03:28,433 --> 00:03:30,200
Well, what did you expect?

63
00:03:30,200 --> 00:03:31,867
I am the daughter of a general.

64
00:03:31,867 --> 00:03:34,467
Why do you
know how to fight?

65
00:03:34,467 --> 00:03:35,633
Long story.

66
00:03:35,633 --> 00:03:41,933
[TENSE MUSIC CONTINUES]

67
00:03:41,933 --> 00:03:43,433
You two will regret this!

68
00:03:43,433 --> 00:03:44,667
- Really?!
- We'll see!

69
00:03:45,467 --> 00:03:46,567
Fine!

70
00:03:56,867 --> 00:03:59,800
[TENSE MUSIC CONTINUES]

71
00:03:59,800 --> 00:04:03,433
- [GRUNTING, GROANING]
- [BLOWS, KICKS LANDING]

72
00:04:05,833 --> 00:04:06,833
[LOUD THWACK]

73
00:04:09,200 --> 00:04:10,067
[BODY THUDS]

74
00:04:10,067 --> 00:04:12,500
- Yay! Mommy is so awesome!
- Yay!

75
00:04:12,500 --> 00:04:14,367
[KING]
Miss Agnes is great too!

76
00:04:14,367 --> 00:04:18,200
[TENSE MUSIC CONTINUES]

77
00:04:18,200 --> 00:04:21,367
[MUSIC BUILDING UP]

78
00:04:21,367 --> 00:04:28,300
[THRILLING MUSIC PLAYING]

79
00:04:35,433 --> 00:04:36,533
[DOOR CLOSES]

80
00:04:36,533 --> 00:04:37,833
- [KICK LANDS]
- [DOOR SLAMS]

81
00:04:39,700 --> 00:04:40,733
[DOOR CREAKS]

82
00:04:42,267 --> 00:04:43,433
[SAMUEL SCREAMS]

83
00:04:43,433 --> 00:04:45,700
[THRILLING MUSIC CONTINUES]

84
00:04:45,700 --> 00:04:47,467
- [SAMUEL GRUNTING]
- [LOUD THWACKS]

85
00:04:48,333 --> 00:04:51,233
- [BLOWS LANDING]
- [GROANING]

86
00:04:54,367 --> 00:04:55,733
[LOUD THUDS]

87
00:04:56,600 --> 00:04:57,667
Argh!

88
00:04:59,500 --> 00:05:00,867
[BREATHES HEAVILY, SCREAMS]

89
00:05:01,733 --> 00:05:04,400
- [BLOWS LANDING]
- [GROANING]

90
00:05:04,400 --> 00:05:05,467
[LOUD THUD]

91
00:05:05,467 --> 00:05:12,400
[THRILLING MUSIC CONTINUES]

92
00:05:14,733 --> 00:05:15,733
[LOUD THUD]

93
00:05:19,967 --> 00:05:21,667
[KICKS LANDING]

94
00:05:24,733 --> 00:05:25,900
[LOUD THWACK]

95
00:05:27,267 --> 00:05:30,267
[THRILLING MUSIC CONTINUES]

96
00:05:30,267 --> 00:05:32,000
[CLOTHES HANGERS CLATTERING]

97
00:05:35,667 --> 00:05:36,867
[HEAVY THUD]

98
00:05:39,433 --> 00:05:40,533
[GRUNTS]

99
00:05:41,433 --> 00:05:46,800
[GROANING]

100
00:05:46,800 --> 00:05:53,767
- [SAMUEL GRUNTING, SCREAMING]
- [THRILLING MUSIC CONTINUES]

101
00:05:53,767 --> 00:05:55,900
[BREATHING HEAVILY]

102
00:05:59,467 --> 00:06:00,467
Try me!

103
00:06:01,400 --> 00:06:02,433
Wait!

104
00:06:03,433 --> 00:06:05,400
My name is
Atty. Leah Ramirez-Rivera.

105
00:06:05,933 --> 00:06:07,833
I am the wife of Jacob Rivera.

106
00:06:07,867 --> 00:06:11,533
I am the daughter
of Police General Diego Ramirez.

107
00:06:11,533 --> 00:06:13,433
They are your bosses,
aren't they?

108
00:06:13,433 --> 00:06:15,367
[GLOOMY MUSIC PLAYING]

109
00:06:15,367 --> 00:06:16,633
What?

110
00:06:16,633 --> 00:06:18,767
Are you going to kill someone
important to your bosses?

111
00:06:19,500 --> 00:06:20,567
Answer me!

112
00:06:23,467 --> 00:06:24,600
So, it's true?

113
00:06:26,000 --> 00:06:27,100
[EXCLAIMS]

114
00:06:27,100 --> 00:06:28,867
- [KICK, BLOW LAND]
- [BODY THUDS]

115
00:06:28,867 --> 00:06:29,933
[HUFFS]

116
00:06:29,933 --> 00:06:30,933
[STIRRING MUSIC PLAYING]

117
00:06:30,933 --> 00:06:33,600
King, Chloe! Get in the car!

118
00:06:34,633 --> 00:06:36,800
- Hurry up!
- Hang on...

119
00:06:36,800 --> 00:06:37,967
- King!
- Wait!

120
00:06:37,967 --> 00:06:39,467
Wait a minute!

121
00:06:39,467 --> 00:06:41,467
Where are you taking
my grandson?!

122
00:06:42,667 --> 00:06:44,167
- [AGNES] King!
- King!

123
00:06:44,167 --> 00:06:45,667
- Grandma!
- Leah!

124
00:06:45,667 --> 00:06:47,000
He's safer with me!

125
00:06:47,000 --> 00:06:49,400
No! You can't take my grandson!

126
00:06:49,400 --> 00:06:51,500
Listen to me! I didn't make
this decision alone.

127
00:06:51,500 --> 00:06:54,700
Samuel called and asked me
to protect our son.

128
00:06:54,700 --> 00:06:56,500
And that's what I intend to do!

129
00:06:56,500 --> 00:06:57,667
No, no, Leah!

130
00:06:57,667 --> 00:06:58,733
No!

131
00:06:58,733 --> 00:07:00,000
- Agnes!
- Give him back!

132
00:07:00,000 --> 00:07:02,000
King! King, wait for me!

133
00:07:02,000 --> 00:07:03,133
Leah, no!

134
00:07:03,133 --> 00:07:06,033
- Grandma! Grandma!
- King! Leah, don't do this!

135
00:07:06,033 --> 00:07:08,167
- King! King!
- [TIRES SCREECHING]

136
00:07:08,167 --> 00:07:09,500
Grandma!

137
00:07:11,400 --> 00:07:17,800
[OMINOUS MUSIC PLAYING]

138
00:07:17,833 --> 00:07:18,833
- [LOUD THWACK]
- Argh--

139
00:07:28,000 --> 00:07:29,367
Your order, ma'am.

140
00:07:31,000 --> 00:07:31,833
Thank you.

141
00:07:31,833 --> 00:07:33,967
Judith, could you help me?
Sorry.

142
00:07:37,900 --> 00:07:38,900
Enzo...

143
00:07:40,500 --> 00:07:41,500
Arissa.

144
00:07:42,533 --> 00:07:44,400
Don't worry too much about Enzo.

145
00:07:44,400 --> 00:07:46,200
He goes off the radar
every now and then.

146
00:07:46,200 --> 00:07:48,033
- Once--
- Luke, can you stop?

147
00:07:48,067 --> 00:07:49,533
You don't know anything!

148
00:07:49,533 --> 00:07:51,400
Yeah, I don't know.

149
00:07:52,600 --> 00:07:54,433
Because you never
tell me anything.

150
00:07:54,433 --> 00:07:56,433
So how would I know?

151
00:07:56,433 --> 00:07:58,700
Did I do something wrong,
Arissa?

152
00:07:58,700 --> 00:08:00,867
Why can't you open up to me?

153
00:08:02,867 --> 00:08:04,067
Tell me.

154
00:08:04,067 --> 00:08:09,200
[SINISTER MUSIC PLAYING]

155
00:08:09,200 --> 00:08:10,667
Nothing.

156
00:08:12,133 --> 00:08:15,767
Don't tell me you believe
the lies about my dad

157
00:08:15,767 --> 00:08:17,033
on social media.

158
00:08:18,900 --> 00:08:20,433
So that's it.

159
00:08:21,000 --> 00:08:23,600
That's why you've been keeping
your distance from me.

160
00:08:23,600 --> 00:08:27,767
I'm telling you,
none of it is true.

161
00:08:27,767 --> 00:08:28,767
[SINISTER MUSIC CONTINUES]

162
00:08:28,767 --> 00:08:30,533
It's just fake news.

163
00:08:31,600 --> 00:08:35,033
My father is a good
and honest congressman.

164
00:08:35,933 --> 00:08:37,133
- Luke--
- I'm sure.

165
00:08:41,767 --> 00:08:44,100
Arissa, we need to go.
Right now.

166
00:08:44,100 --> 00:08:45,033
I'm sorry.

167
00:08:46,733 --> 00:08:47,733
[DOOR OPENS]

168
00:08:47,733 --> 00:08:54,633
[STIRRING MUSIC PLAYING]

169
00:08:55,933 --> 00:08:57,900
[OBJECTS CLATTERING]

170
00:08:59,200 --> 00:09:00,833
- [GRUNTS]
- [LOUD THWACK]

171
00:09:00,833 --> 00:09:07,733
[UNSETTLING MUSIC PLAYING]

172
00:09:13,600 --> 00:09:20,567
[GRIM MUSIC PLAYING]

173
00:09:26,200 --> 00:09:27,267
Sir?

174
00:09:30,067 --> 00:09:31,033
Sir!

175
00:09:31,033 --> 00:09:33,967
[SUSPENSEFUL MUSIC PLAYING]

176
00:09:33,967 --> 00:09:35,000
Sir!

177
00:09:36,800 --> 00:09:37,833
[SAMUEL] Sir Enrico!

178
00:09:37,833 --> 00:09:38,800
Sir!

179
00:09:39,300 --> 00:09:40,300
Colonel!

180
00:09:41,067 --> 00:09:42,300
Drop your gun!

181
00:09:42,300 --> 00:09:44,133
- [JOHNNY] Drop it! Now!
- No!

182
00:09:44,133 --> 00:09:45,867
- No!
- Drop it!

183
00:09:45,867 --> 00:09:48,167
Sir, looks like
the Colonel is dead!

184
00:09:48,967 --> 00:09:50,200
You bastard.

185
00:09:50,200 --> 00:09:51,833
You killed Colonel Villanueva!

186
00:09:51,833 --> 00:09:52,867
I didn't kill him!

187
00:09:52,867 --> 00:09:54,133
Put your gun down!

188
00:09:54,833 --> 00:09:55,800
Drop it!

189
00:09:56,567 --> 00:09:57,667
Slowly!

190
00:09:57,667 --> 00:10:01,167
[SUSPENSEFUL MUSIC CONTINUES]

191
00:10:01,200 --> 00:10:02,200
Come on!

192
00:10:03,233 --> 00:10:04,633
Johnny...

193
00:10:05,000 --> 00:10:06,900
- Johnny, I didn't kill him.
- [GUN CLATTERS]

194
00:10:06,900 --> 00:10:08,200
Who are you?

195
00:10:08,200 --> 00:10:09,667
Take off your mask!

196
00:10:11,233 --> 00:10:12,633
Take it off!

197
00:10:15,700 --> 00:10:17,200
I said take it off!

198
00:10:17,200 --> 00:10:18,300
[HUFFING]

199
00:10:19,167 --> 00:10:22,867
[SUSPENSEFUL MUSIC CONTINUES]

200
00:10:22,867 --> 00:10:24,267
Samuel Trinidad?

201
00:10:24,267 --> 00:10:26,233
Damn it! I knew it!

202
00:10:26,233 --> 00:10:27,867
Johnny, I didn't kill him.

203
00:10:27,867 --> 00:10:29,567
- Believe me--
- [BLOW LANDS]

204
00:10:29,567 --> 00:10:31,567
[GRUNTS, BREATHES HEAVILY]

205
00:10:32,200 --> 00:10:34,300
Turn around.
Give me your hands.

206
00:10:36,233 --> 00:10:38,067
Johnny, I didn't do it!

207
00:10:38,067 --> 00:10:39,800
You're going to rot in jail.

208
00:10:39,800 --> 00:10:42,200
You're a scammer,
and now you're a murderer, too.

209
00:10:42,200 --> 00:10:43,867
I didn't kill him!

210
00:10:43,867 --> 00:10:45,733
[BREATHING HEAVILY]
Sir... Sir...

211
00:10:47,133 --> 00:10:48,200
[SAMUEL] Sir...

212
00:10:52,267 --> 00:10:53,733
- [SUSPENSEFUL MUSIC PLAYING]
- Matthias,

213
00:10:53,733 --> 00:10:56,433
delete all the CCTV footage

214
00:10:56,433 --> 00:10:58,933
so the cops don't get anything.

215
00:10:58,933 --> 00:11:00,267
I'll take care of it.

216
00:11:04,033 --> 00:11:05,467
Where is Enzo?

217
00:11:05,467 --> 00:11:07,467
I didn't take your son!

218
00:11:07,500 --> 00:11:09,767
It was Trinidad's idea

219
00:11:09,767 --> 00:11:12,967
to get you out from hiding!

220
00:11:12,967 --> 00:11:14,433
[TAPS LOUDLY]

221
00:11:15,467 --> 00:11:17,733
If he's not with you,
where the heck is my son?!

222
00:11:28,067 --> 00:11:30,833
[METAL DOOR CREAKS]

223
00:11:30,833 --> 00:11:33,433
[BEKKAH] Get them out of there!
Quickly! Quickly!

224
00:11:39,667 --> 00:11:41,833
Go! Get down! Hurry up!

225
00:11:41,867 --> 00:11:43,467
- Quit idling!
- Come on.

226
00:11:45,167 --> 00:11:48,833
Are you sure
no one followed you here?

227
00:11:48,833 --> 00:11:49,800
Get down!

228
00:11:49,800 --> 00:11:51,000
I'm sure.

229
00:11:51,000 --> 00:11:52,600
Are you sure?

230
00:11:52,800 --> 00:11:54,667
Guaranteed, ma'am.

231
00:11:54,667 --> 00:11:55,967
- Good job.
- Get down!

232
00:12:01,533 --> 00:12:04,800
Johnny, believe me!
I didn't do it!

233
00:12:04,800 --> 00:12:06,000
I didn't kill Colonel!

234
00:12:06,000 --> 00:12:07,633
We were together
in this operation!

235
00:12:07,633 --> 00:12:09,100
Do you really think
I'm that stupid?!

236
00:12:09,100 --> 00:12:10,933
You're caught in the act!
Quit lying!

237
00:12:10,933 --> 00:12:11,967
- Johnny!
- What?!

238
00:12:11,967 --> 00:12:14,000
The girls in the container van,

239
00:12:14,000 --> 00:12:16,767
Johnny, I saved them.

240
00:12:16,800 --> 00:12:20,533
A man came
and stopped the truck.

241
00:12:20,533 --> 00:12:21,867
Those programmer dudes,

242
00:12:21,867 --> 00:12:24,833
I stopped them
from being kidnapped.

243
00:12:24,833 --> 00:12:27,000
From those recruiters.
Johnny, that was me!

244
00:12:27,967 --> 00:12:29,633
[CAR DOOR OPENS]

245
00:12:32,700 --> 00:12:34,600
You call me Zorro.

246
00:12:36,033 --> 00:12:37,367
Remove your helmet!

247
00:12:39,033 --> 00:12:40,167
You're Zorro?

248
00:12:41,967 --> 00:12:45,200
I entered that syndicate
to take them down!

249
00:12:45,200 --> 00:12:48,633
Johnny, Bakunawa is just a setup
done by their boss.

250
00:12:48,667 --> 00:12:50,800
The Old Man did it
for revenge!

251
00:12:51,867 --> 00:12:53,967
- Johnny, believe me!
- Who's the Old Man?

252
00:12:55,733 --> 00:12:58,133
It's General Diego Ramirez.

253
00:13:00,033 --> 00:13:01,800
Your father is the Old Man.

254
00:13:04,500 --> 00:13:05,633
Policarpio!

255
00:13:06,867 --> 00:13:07,833
Policarpio!

256
00:13:07,833 --> 00:13:10,133
What are you doing?
Get him in the car!

257
00:13:12,500 --> 00:13:13,767
Johnny, I didn't do this!

258
00:13:13,767 --> 00:13:16,600
Johnny! Johnny,
I didn't do this!

259
00:13:16,600 --> 00:13:18,100
Let's go!

260
00:13:18,100 --> 00:13:21,200
The alleged leader
of Bakunawa has been arrested.

261
00:13:21,200 --> 00:13:22,400
The syndicate behind

262
00:13:22,433 --> 00:13:25,133
the country's widespread
scamming activities.

263
00:13:25,133 --> 00:13:28,767
It's Samuel Trinidad, son of
the late scammer Mike Trinidad.

264
